simply-journal-admin (2.0.0-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Bundle an embedded Python runtime under /opt/simply-journal-admin/python
    instead of depending on the target host's interpreter.
  * Unpack the project wheel under /opt/simply-journal-admin/app and add a
    /usr/bin/simply-journal-admin wrapper that invokes the embedded runtime.
  * Keep the package CLI-only; do not register a systemd service during
    installation.
  * Remove install-time pip, virtualenv creation, and internet access.

 -- Modern Python Engineering <maintainers@example.invalid>  Tue, 16 Jun 2026 00:00:00 +0000

